metadata.name: Deeply, truly, freely.
metadata.description:
Deep contact that provides the foundation to freely express each other's true intentions with your touch and breath. Eyes full of acceptance that sends you higher than heaven. All by itself. Deepest connection at the core of your souls gives freedoms of expression and growth that you both need.
All of it is in this art inspire by me, created by Yulia Tauritari with Svetlana Keyer as the model.
